<note><title>二进制数组</title><content><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd">
<en-note><div>WebGL项目：</div><div>- 显卡与浏览器之间的通信接口</div><div>- 起因：JS与显卡间大量的、实时的数据交换，他们间的数据通信必须是二进制的，而不是传统的文本格式</div><div>- 需要引入一种机制直接操作字节，使4字节的32位整数，以二进制的形式直接传入显卡</div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" face="Helvetica Neue">- <span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; float: none;">二进制数组就是在这种背景下诞生的。它很像C语言的数组，允许开发者以数组下标的形式，直接操作内存，大大增强了JavaScript处理二进制数据的能力，使得开发者有可能通过JavaScript与操作系统的原生接口进行二进制通信</span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; float: none;"><br/></span></font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">二进制数组的三个对象：</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">1.ArrayBuffer</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">2.TypedAarry</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">3.DataView</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222"><br/></font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">二进制数组的应用：</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">1.AJAX</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">2.Canvas</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">3.WebSocket</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">4.Fetch API</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222">5.FIle API</font></div><div style="orphans: 2; widows: 2;"><font face="Helvetica Neue" color="#222222"><br/></font></div></en-note>
]]></content><created>20170804T041004Z</created><updated>20170804T043430Z</updated><note-attributes><latitude>31.98610455224786</latitude><longitude>118.7587797209424</longitude><altitude>61.32246017456055</altitude><author>18851280888@163.com</author><source>desktop.mac</source><reminder-order>0</reminder-order></note-attributes></note>
